localString.value: These dark undead seek to destroy all life, filling graveyards with their victims and populating the world with their horrid progeny.
Their time-shriveled features hidden beneath centuries-old funereal wrappings, these former kings and high priests, now undead, continue to stand guard over their places of rest.
This door was the main entrance on the mesa, but now its been sealed by the elements. No passage through here.
This will block portalling into the area via the temple portal and out of the area via the pendant. Place anywhere in the area to be protected.
